clude: \':hidden\'"><div class="fm-sec half_rhythm no_top_margin"><div class="fm-citation half_rhythm no_top_margin clearfix"><div class="inline_block eight_col va_top"><div><div><span class="cit"><span id="pmcmata">Environ Health Perspect</span>. 2004 Nov; 112(15): 1550\xe2\x80\x931556. </span></div><div><span class="fm-vol-iss-date">Published online 2004 Jul 27. </span>  <span class="doi">doi:\xc2\xa0<a href="//dx.doi.org/10.1289%2Fehp.7117" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=1247620&amp;issue-id=122852&amp;journal-id=253&amp;FROM=Article%7CFront%20Matter&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CCrosslink%7CDOI">10.1289/ehp.7117</a></span></div></div></div><div class="inline_block four_col va_top show-overflow align_right"><div class="fm-citation-ids"><div class="fm-citation-pmcid"><span class="fm-citation-ids-label">PMCID: </span><span>PMC1247620</span></div><div class="fm-citation-pmid">PMID: <a href="/pubmed/15531441">15531441</a></div></div></div><div class="fm-dochead no_margin">Research</div><div class="fm-doctopic no_margin">Articles</div></div><h1 class="content-title">Understanding the Spatial Clustering of Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome (SARS) in Hong Kong</h1><div class="half_rhythm"><div class="contrib-group fm-author"><a href="/pubmed/?term=Lai%20P%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=15531441" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140229615732000" co-class="co-affbox">P.C. Lai</a>,<sup>1</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Wong%20C%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=15531441" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140229600989712" co-class="co-affbox">C.M. Wong</a>,<sup>2</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Hedley%20A%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=15531441" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140229598132016" co-class="co-affbox">A.J. Hedley</a>,<sup>2</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Lo%20S%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=15531441" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140229652498928" co-class="co-affbox">S.V. Lo</a>,<sup>3</sup> <a href